{"type":"answer","id":256976,"parentType":"question","parentId":24771,"uid":23714,"contents":"这两款浏览器，各有各的好处。Firefox 开源，支持的平台更多；Chrome 易用性更好，目前用户更多。<br>\n对安全性要求较高的用户，Firefox 更合适。<br>\n需要注意：【不要】下载使用“谋智中国”定制版，建议使用英文版。<br>\n<br>\n引申阅读：<br>\n<a href=\"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2018/09/Why-You-Should-Switch-from-Chrome-to-Firefox.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">《弃用 Chrome 改用 Firefox 的几点理由——关于 Chrome 69 隐私丑闻的随想》</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2018/10/How-to-Choose-Firefox-Version.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">《基于安全性考虑，如何选择及切换 Firefox 版本？》</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2016/10/custom-firefox-theme-without-extension.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">《无需任何插件或扩展，定制 Firefox 外观》</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2019/07/Customize-Firefox.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">《扫盲 Firefox 定制——从“user.js”到“omni.ja”》</a>","date":"2020-05-05","agreeCount":1,"discussionCount":0}